   "body" : "I can use this code to extract btcaddress from Txout, but I don't know how to extract address from Txin:\n\n```\nBOOST_FOREACH(const CTxOut& txout, tx.vout) {\n      if(ExtractDestination(txout.scriptPubKey, addressRetout)){\n                std::string bitaddrout = CBitcoinAddress(addressRetout).ToString();\n       }\n}\n```\n\nAnd I have try this code to extract address from Txin, but it not work:\n\n```\n BOOST_FOREACH(const CTxIn& txin, tx.vin)   \n{ \n    COutPoint prevout = txin.prevout;\n    CCoins prev;\n    if(pcoinsTip->GetCoins(prevout.hash, prev))\n    {\n        if (prevout.n < prev.vout.size()){\n            const CTxOut &vout = prev.vout[prevout.n];   \n            if (ExtractDestination(vout.scriptPubKey, addressRetin))\n            {\n                std::string bitaddrin = CBitcoinAddress(addressRetin).ToString();     \n             }\n         }\n    }   \n}\n```\n\nthe function \"ExtractDestination(vout.scriptPubKey, addressRetin)\" always return 0.\n",
